NEWS FLASH - PUBLIC NOTICE OF STRATEGIC PLANNING MEETING

  1. Strategic Planning Public Notice.pdf


  1. Mayor’s Message

    Thank you for visiting the Amery “City of Lakes” website. Be sure to check out our Facebook page!

    My name is Paul Isakson and I am a long time Amery resident. I was educated in the Amery School District and graduated from UW-Eau Claire. My wife Kate and I have been married for 30 years. Our 3 daughters also attended the Amery school system.

    Read More



  1. Economic Development
    The Amery Economic Development Corporation is in the business of creating business for the greater Amery area, and enhancing Amery's long-term prosperity and quality of life.

    Read More

  1. Visit Amery

    Amery is quickly gaining fame as one of the most spectacular summer vacation spots in the Midwest. But those heart-stopping views of sky, water and land don’t simply disappear after Labor Day.
